# 🔄 6. Temporal Workflow Prompt

*(Used to create long-running business workflows)*

```
Generate Temporal workflows
for a NestJS TypeScript backend
for an Insurance Policy Configuration Platform.

Create workflows:

QUOTE WORKFLOW

Lifecycle:
DRAFT → QUOTED → SUBMITTED → UNDER_REVIEW → APPROVED → REJECTED → ISSUED

Steps:

Risk Profiling
Premium Calculation
Rule Evaluation
Underwriting Review

If risk_score > threshold
require Senior Underwriter approval.

CLAIM WORKFLOW

Lifecycle:
SUBMITTED → VALIDATION_PENDING → UNDER_INVESTIGATION → FRAUD_REVIEW → ASSESSMENT → APPROVED → REJECTED → FINANCE_REVIEW → PAID → CLOSED

Steps:

Policy validation
Coverage validation
Waiting period check
Duplicate claim detection

If claim_amount > 3x average
trigger fraud review.

Generate:

Workflow definitions
Activities
Worker setup
Retry logic
Compensation handling
```

